MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2006-1055. State ex rel. Rashada v. Pianka.

Cuyahoga App. No. 87450, 2006-Ohio-2584. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellant’s second and third motions for temporary restraining order,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motions are denied.
